some points from my experience.

I am in csh, so to set the env variable do 
setenv JULIA_CUDA_MEMORY_POOL none

] doit etre tap√©, c'est pas ok un copier/coller !!

julia --project=. 


pour lancer mon .jl de test en interactif : julia --project ocean_hydro_only_test.jl test true


run in interactive mode : 
with gpu

qsub -I -q gpuq -l walltime=00:30:00


with mpi 
qsub -I -q mpi_1 -l select=1:ncpus=28:mpiprocs=28:mem=120g -l walltime=12:00:00
